{
  "texts": [
    "When recruiting our reappraisers our preregistered goal was to obtain 100 human reappraisals for each of the 18 vignettes.",
    "We thereby recruited 200 participants to reappraise nine random vignettes each.",
    "Two hundred participants completed the task.",
    "We removed three participants during analyses for providing nonsensical responses that were not at all related to the content of the vignettes.",
    "Our final sample included 197 participants (77 female, 119 male, 1 nonbinary; age: M = 40.50 years, SD = 13.42)."
  ]
}